data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Frederick, Colorado! This charming ranch-style residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a host of impressive features, this property is a true gem. Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of natural light that floods the living spaces, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing a spacious and flexible layout for both everyday living and entertaining.The kitchen boasts high-end appliances, granite countertops, and custom cabinets that not only provide ample storage but also add a touch of sophistication to the space. One of the standout features of this property is its quick access to I-25 and Highway 85, making your commute a breeze and opening up endless possibilities for exploring the surrounding areas. Convenience meets comfort in this fantastic location, allowing you to enjoy both the peaceful charm of Frederick and the accessibility to major transportation routes. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of modern living, thoughtful design, and convenient location in Frederick, Colorado.
